sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / CI
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant RHOAI as RHOAI Operator<br/>DataScienceCluster
    participant Kueue as Kueue Controller<br/>Workload Admission
    participant TrainOp as Training Operator<br/>PyTorchJob
    participant TrainerV2 as Trainer v2<br/>TrainJob
    participant JobSet as JobSet Controller<br/>JobSet
    participant KubeRay as KubeRay Operator<br/>RayCluster/RayJob
    participant Master as Master Pod<br/>29500/TCP c10d
    participant Worker as Worker Pods<br/>dynamic/TCP NCCL
    participant RayHead as Ray Head<br/>6379/TCP GCS<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    participant RayWorker as Ray Workers<br/>8076/TCP Object Store
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+

    Note over User,S3: Flow 1: Distributed PyTorch Training (PyTorchJob)
    User->>K8sAPI: POST PyTorchJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>TrainOp: Watch event: PyTorchJob created
    TrainOp->>K8sAPI: Create Master + Worker Pods<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Worker->>S3: Download training data<br/>Auth: AWS IAM credentials
    Worker->>Worker: NCCL AllReduce<br/>dynamic/TCP plaintext
    Worker->>Master: Rendezvous<br/>29500/TCP c10d plaintext
    Master-->>K8sAPI: Update PyTorchJob status

    Note over User,S3: Flow 2: Ray-based Distributed Training (RayJob)
    User->>K8sAPI: POST RayJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>KubeRay: Watch event: RayJob created
    KubeRay->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster (Head + Workers)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    RayHead->>RayWorker: GCS protocol<br/>6379/TCP plaintext
    RayWorker->>RayHead: Object store<br/>8076/TCP plaintext
    User->>RayHead: Submit job via Dashboard<br/>8265/TCP HTTP plaintext
    RayWorker->>S3: Upload/download data<br/>443/TCP HTTPS AWS IAM
    RayHead-->>User: Job status + logs<br/>8265/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,S3: Flow 3: Kueue-Managed Training
    User->>K8sAPI: POST PyTorchJob/TrainJob<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Kueue: Workload created (admission pending)
    Kueue->>K8sAPI: Admit Workload<br/>(ClusterQueue quota check)
    K8sAPI->>TrainOp: PyTorchJob unsuspended
    TrainOp->>K8sAPI: Create training Pods

    Note over User,S3: Flow 4: Kubeflow Trainer v2 (TrainJob + JobSet)
    User->>K8sAPI: POST TrainJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>TrainerV2: Watch event: TrainJob created
    TrainerV2->>K8sAPI: Create JobSet<br/>+ ClusterTrainingRuntime ref
    K8sAPI->>JobSet: Watch event: JobSet created
    JobSet->>K8sAPI: Create coordinated Jobs
    Worker->>Worker: NCCL/RDMA AllReduce<br/>dynamic/TCP plaintext

    Note over User,HF: Model Download Flow
    Worker->>HF: Download pre-trained model<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (HF_TOKEN)
    HF-->>Worker: Model artifacts
